OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA day of sunshine and blustery
OL,6,Fshowers, with the showers possibly
OL,7,Fturning heavy in places. An isolated
OL,8,Fchance of thunder in the north of the
OL,9,Fregion. Temperatures a little below
OL,10,Faverage.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FShowers becoming less
OL,13,Ffrequent into the evening, before
OL,14,Fskies cloud over from the west later
OL,15,Fin the night, with showery outbreaks
OL,16,Fof rain reaching the region towards
OL,17,Fdawn.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
