OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FCloudy with showery
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain during the morning,
OL,7,Fsome sunny or bright spells
OL,8,Fdeveloping, however a continue risk of
OL,9,Fshowers with hail and thunder, before
OL,10,Fthese fade towards evening.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FA
OL,13,Fspell of wet and windy weather moves
OL,14,Fin for Thursday. Largely cloudy on
OL,15,FFriday with patchy rain. High pressure
OL,16,Fdeveloping from Saturday bringing
OL,17,Fsunny spells and rising temperatures.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
